Whether it just makes you feel good or you want to pay it forward, whats most important is giving to a cause that you verified is genuine. The secondary layer of “analysis” that looks into whether you are giving only to the most needy I think is moot. As long as there is a social need being addressed

Whether it just makes you feel good or you want to pay it forward, whats most important is giving to a cause that you verified is genuine. The secondary layer of “analysis” that looks into whether you are giving only to the most needy I think is moot. As long as there is a social need being addressed, crowdfunding can be effective.